Telmex Tools inventory 

1.Introduction



1.1 Purpose

The purpose of this software product is to solve the manual processes that are carried out in Telmex managing their work tools which represent several problems of time and costs.

The difficulties of using paper for tools inventory represents an extra effort that can be substituted with automatization.

  1.2 Scope

The benefits of the inventory are the automatization of the processes and give efficiency to them by managing all the available tools in real time using software.

The software is meant to be as a personal tool inside a large company.


1.3 Definitions

Definitions, acronyms, and abbreviations:

